Oli has been taking a stand to continue Finance Minister Yubaraj Khatiwada by reappointing him to the upper house. The Prime Minister had hinted that in a recent interview.","title":"NCP Vice-chair Gautam demands to nominate him to National Assembly - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/31/124135/","video":[]}
